---
title: Pineapple Pork Chops with Snap Peas and Jasmine Rice
description: Pineapple proved that it could conquer pizza. Now we’re helping it take it’s sweet–savory domination to the next level. Pineapple salsa smothers these pork chops, with the fruit’s tangy juices mingling with those of the pork. You’ll wanna scoot the jasmine rice and snap peas over on your plate so that they can soak up some of that bright yellow sunshine, too.
